# Cursor Rules for Skill Sorter Project

## Work Log Rule
- **ALWAYS** write to `WORK_LOG.md` after making any changes to the codebase
- Describe what was changed, added, or modified
- Include a brief description of the change
- Use bullet points for multiple changes
- Be specific about what files were affected and why
- **Add newest entries at the bottom** of the work log (no dates needed)

## Code Style
- Use consistent formatting and indentation
- Follow React best practices
- Use meaningful variable and function names
- Add comments for complex logic

## Project Structure
- Keep UI components in `src/components/ui/`
- Use the `@/` alias for imports from the `src/` directory
- Maintain the existing file organization 